channel.title: Protokol
channel.description:
I was just chatting with someone on MSN when the subject came up about Protokol, We were discussing about his detailed knowledge of Java, his infilitration into people's good graces with things such as Kaitnieks Wallpaper and a rather packed Walkthrough. We were starting to mull over whether he was a JageX Double Agent because he suddenly and "mysteriously" left on Nov 18 after he might have managed to find out some info. Doesn't it seem odd that someone after joining for 2 months managed to become a mod?
Discuss.
